{"tid":2062922,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"貿易協議中國「一半都無法履行」 美參議員要貿易代表給答覆","createTime":"2020-06-13T13:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T14:58:45.000Z","uid":75656,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3dcb4de3465f704c8d9b3f41da80c22b593a0d6f","tid":2062922,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:26:18.000Z","msg":"繼日前受訪時稱，美國握有中國企圖妨礙美國武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫苗研究的證據後，參議院史考特（Rick Scott）今天再批中國，於推特上公佈致函美國貿易代表辦公室（USTR）的信件，稱中國在落實美中第1階段貿易協議「連一半都達不到」，要求貿易代表萊席爾（Robert Lighthizer）就此給出答覆。<br />\n<br />\n史考特在信中引述智庫彼得森國際經濟研究所（PIIE）於本月6日發佈的報告，指截至4月為止，中國在履行協議上「嚴重落後」，而且連原定進程的一半都達不到，不單如此，這段期間中國依然大力推動出口，5月的出超額還從4月的453.4億美元大增至629.3億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3196726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3196726&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=3c9586e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3196726&h=97ea6034\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3196726</a>"},{"pid":"d2d593f4ebd529c75ca747143a32d291217997c4","tid":2062922,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:30:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f875731ca7acbf886dc44a78da4bc949394e3d61","tid":2062922,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:31:24.000Z","msg":"美帝想開波啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e557541d0421f4084016927442bf3653e4531d","tid":2062922,"uid":37413,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:47:03.000Z","msg":"預咗㗎啦，跟著又扮傾，之後傾妥又唔履行，跟著又傾.....係咁loop，唔履行又如何，打鳩我吖笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本就想拖到侵任期完睇吓下一任有冇得收買"},{"pid":"83a175811ab4a12a919d8b1084dd44f782c7d311","tid":2062922,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"s